scale function.

Signed-off-by: Ionela Voinescu <ionela.voinescu@arm.com>
Signed-off-by: Dietmar Eggemann <dietmar.eggemann@arm.com>
Signed-off-by: Quentin Perret <quentin.perret@arm.com>
